ssing souls a second time.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_132809\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_finalsoul.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-132809\" data-attachment-id=\"132809\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/02/27/enshrouded-after-the-dragon/es15_finalsoul/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_finalsoul.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1900,1067\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES15_FinalSoul\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;The jumping puzzle to get to this one was a chore\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_finalsoul.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_finalsoul.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_finalsoul.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_finalsoul.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_finalsoul.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_finalsoul.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_finalsoul.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_finalsoul.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-132809\"\u003eThe jumping puzzle to get to this one was a chore\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBut some of the other ones… maybe?  I have only lit 4 of the 8 balefires needed to summon the dragon that we fought last time around.  I assume that I could go click on the other 4 and get credit.  But those don’t all grant something beyond xp, so maybe I should hold off on those\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWell, there is always exploration.  The hand crafted map in \u003cem\u003eEnshrouded\u003c/em\u003e is excellent for exploration.  To start with, there is stuff squirreled away all over the map.  I keep an axe in my primary tool bar because there is often a suspicious bookcase covering a secret passage or hidden alcove, or maybe a flimsy wooden barrier behind which you might spy the gleam of a hidden chest.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere isn’t a hidden bounty in every room you will visit, but it is there in enough rooms than you may feel the need to check them all… and break apart every bookcase to be sure.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLikewise, there isn’t a chest buried in every pile of rubble… and sometimes it is pretty obvious when there is one there.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_132811\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_chestrubblewithflag.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-132811\" data-attachment-id=\"132811\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/02/27/enshrouded-after-the-dragon/es15_chestrubblewithflag/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_chestrubblewithflag.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1894,1055\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES15_ChestRubbleWithFlag\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;A pile of rubble with a banner in it is a give away\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_chestrubblewithflag.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_chestrubblewithflag.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_chestrubblewithflag.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_chestrubblewithflag.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_chestrubblewithflag.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_chestrubblewithflag.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_chestrubblewithflag.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_chestrubblewithflag.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-132811\"\u003eA pile of rubble with a banner in it is a give away\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAnd sometimes it is that pile of rubble in a dark niche in the back of a cave that has a chest.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_132808\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_hiddenrubble.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-132808\" data-attachment-id=\"132808\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/02/27/enshrouded-after-the-dragon/es15_hiddenrubble/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_hiddenrubble.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1647,984\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES15_HiddenRubble\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Found it\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_hiddenrubble.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_hiddenrubble.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_hiddenrubble.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_hiddenrubble.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_hiddenrubble.jpg?w=1198 1198w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_hiddenrubble.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_hiddenrubble.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_hiddenrubble.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-132808\"\u003eFound it\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThen there is the rubble that hides passages to other locations.  If it is a place they really want you to go there can be an explosive barrel or two placed to suggest that maybe you should blow this particular bit of rubble sky high.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGo after all the rubble!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eExploration also gets you to the various bits of lore seeded throughout the game world.  The journal also has a lore section that will tell you what you have seen and what is still out there to find.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_132822\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lorepage.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-132822\" data-attachment-id=\"132822\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/02/27/enshrouded-after-the-dragon/es15_lorepage/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lorepage.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2087,1175\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES15_LorePage\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Tracking the various lore pieces\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lorepage.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lorepage.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lorepage.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lorepage.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lorepage.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lorepage.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lorepage.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lorepage.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-132822\"\u003eTracking the various lore pieces\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThose also give you a bit of xp when you find them… but mostly tell you the story of the world and what happened.  For me it is like so much quest text, even when I read it I still forget it almost immediately, but somebody out there probably loves that.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe world itself is also pretty and interesting and has a variety of scenery that is worth seeking out, if that is your thing.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_132824\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_icelake.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-132824\" data-attachment-id=\"132824\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/02/27/enshrouded-after-the-dragon/es15_icelake/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_icelake.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2560,1349\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES15_IceLake\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Our group out crossing an ice lake\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_icelake.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_icelake.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_icelake.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"316\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_icelake.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_icelake.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_icelake.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_icelake.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_icelake.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-132824\"\u003eOur group out crossing an ice lake\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAbove the ice lake is a large frozen waterfall… which, to my chagrin, does not have a cave behind it.  At least not that I have found so far.  But I got out my pick axe to try.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe most rewarding… at least in terms of character progression… things to find are the various shroud roots hidden throughout the land.  Chopping those down shroud roots earns you skill points.  That was what we were out doing last weekend, chasing down some of the remaining ones we had previously missed.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_132826\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_shroudroot.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-132826\" data-attachment-id=\"132826\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/02/27/enshrouded-after-the-dragon/es15_shroudroot/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_shroudroot.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2560,1135\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES15_ShroudRoot\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;A shroud root always looks dramatic\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_shroudroot.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_shroudroot.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_shroudroot.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"266\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_shroudroot.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_shroudroot.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_shroudroot.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_shroudroot.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_shroudroot.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-132826\"\u003eA shroud root always looks dramatic\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSome are hidden deep underground, others are barely hidden at all.  A few are just sitting there, in the shroud, visible if you happen to walk by.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe achievements indicate that I have found all of the shroud roots available.  There are a couple of well hidden ones I spent some time reaching.  We’ll have to have another expedition to get everybody there.  And then we’re kind of done with progress.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI still have a few achievements I could wrap up according to Steam.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_132812\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lockedachievements.png\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-132812\" data-attachment-id=\"132812\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/02/27/enshrouded-after-the-dragon/es15_lockedachievements/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lockedachievements.png\" data-orig-size=\"572,648\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES15_LockedAchievements\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;My remaining achievements \u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lockedachievements.png?w=353\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lockedachievements.png?w=397\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lockedachievements.png?w=397\" alt=\"\" width=\"397\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lockedachievements.png?w=397 397w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lockedachievements.png?w=132 132w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lockedachievements.png?w=353 353w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_lockedachievements.png 572w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 397px) 100vw, 397px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-132812\"\u003eMy remaining achievements\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFinding all the flame shrines and sanctums requires some diligent exploration.  We’ll see if I have it in me.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOtherwise we are down to base building… though base building is a huge feature of the game, so don’t let me undersell that even if it isn’t really my thing, farming some chests for the occasional weapon or ring upgrade, and looking for the remaining pieces for that mosaic we picked up.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_132813\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_themoasic.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-132813\" data-attachment-id=\"132813\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/02/27/enshrouded-after-the-dragon/es15_themoasic/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_themoasic.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2092,1038\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES15_TheMoasic\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;The bard tugging at my sleeve while I admire our progress\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_themoasic.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_themoasic.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_themoasic.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_themoasic.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_themoasic.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_themoasic.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_themoasic.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/es15_themoasic.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-132813\"\u003eThe bard tugging at my sleeve while I admire our progress\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSo there are things to do.  But I also feel a bit of a lull in activity as well.  I don’t want to give it up entirely, not yet, while there is still some exploration to be done, however it also isn’t scratching that all important (to the point of obsession at times) character progression itch.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhich is not to say anything negative about the game.  It has kept us occupied for four months at this point.  It is high on the list of reasons we have not been in \u003cem\u003eCataclysm\u003c/em\u003e.  I recommend it and want to see it completed.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI still have a few more posts about \u003cem\u003eEnshrouded\u003c/em\u003e to go, but the state of play now that we’re reach the level cap and slain the dragon is more of filling in the gaps than seeking new adventures.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
